high_descs: Turn around and go to the table ahead.
Pick up the butter knife on the table, to the right of the lettuce.
Turn left, step forward, then turn right to face the table.
Slice the lettuce on the table.
Turn around to face the sink.
Put the butter knife in the left cabinet, under the sink.
Turn left, step forward, then turn left to face the table.
Pick up a slice of lettuce from the table.
Turn right, move forward, then turn right to go to the fridge.
Chill the slice of lettuce in the fridge.
Turn right, go straight toward the stove, turn right, move forward, then turn left to face the trash bin.
Put the slice of lettuce in the trash bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold slice of lettuce in the trash.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the green table.
Pick up the knife behind the tomato on the table.
Walk to the lettuce on the green table.
Cut up the lettuce on the table.
Turn around and walk to the cabinets below the sink.
Place the knife in the leftmost cabinet below the sink then close the cabinet.
Turn around and walk to the lettuce on the green table.
Pick up a piece of lettuce from the table.
Turn right and walk to the fridge.
Chill the piece of lettuce in the fridge then pick up the piece of lettuce from the fridge and close the fridge.
Turn right and walk to the trash can in front of the window.
Place the lettuce in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled piece of lettuce into the trash can by the window.
